source: crates/daemon/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Unsnooze a message

Usage: mxr unsnooze [OPTIONS] [MESSAGE_ID]...

Arguments:
  [MESSAGE_ID]...

Options:
      --all              Unsnooze all
      --dry-run          Show which messages would be unsnoozed without performing the mutation
      --format <FORMAT>  [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help             Print help
